trans-unit.source: Represents a serializable collection of service metadata in XML form.
trans-unit.target: Serialize할 수 있는 서비스 메타데이터 컬렉션을 XML 형식으로 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet> class contains a collection of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> objects, each of which contains one dialect of metadata in XML form.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet> 클래스는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> 개체 컬렉션을 포함하며, 각 컬렉션은 XML 형식의 메타데이터 언어 하나를 포함합니다.

trans-unit.source: Typically, the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet> class is used to pass a group of XML metadata documents to and from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataImporter> objects, such as <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>.
trans-unit.target: 일반적으로 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet> 클래스는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter> 및 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataImporter> 개체(예: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter> 및 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>)와 XML 메타데이터 문서 그룹을 주고 받는 데 사용됩니다.

trans-unit.source: To create a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet> from a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> object of type <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection>, use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet.%23ctor%2A> constructor.

To obtain a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> object of type <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection>, use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet.MetadataSections%2A> property.

In addition, you can use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet.ReadFrom%2A> method to load a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet> from XML data and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet.WriteTo%2A> method to write the internal metadata to an XML format.
trans-unit.target: 또한 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet.ReadFrom%2A> 메서드를 사용하여 XML 데이터에서 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet>를 로드하고 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSet.WriteTo%2A> 메서드를 사용하여 내부 메타데이터를 XML 형식에 쓸 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: This type implements the structure defined in the WS-MetadataExchange specification.
trans-unit.target: 이 형식은 WS-MetadataExchange 사양에 정의된 구조를 구현합니다.
